Kim_Hyde http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kim_Hyde 0 Kimberly "Kim" Hyde was a fictional character from the Australian soap opera Home and Away, played by Chris Hemsworth. He made his first on screen appearance on 17 February 2004 and departed on 3 July 2007.
